oversee the activities of the Emory Alumni Association (EAA).Learn moreRecords and Transcript RequestThe Office of the University Registrar is available to help you with requests for transcripts, replacement diplomas, enrollment and degree verifications, veteran enrollment services, and more.Learn morethe Emory shield logoNewsEventsNetworksGivingAlumniMiller Ward Alumni HouseResearch PartnershipsFollow us onGive NowVolunteerCopyright & ComplianceEO/AA StatementDonor Privacy Policy